This is used to test the XMeRTL system automatically.  It includes

XtratuM test
PaRTiKle test
FIFO test
SHM test
Trace Test


Before you test the suits, you should change the bellow veriable value:
config.mk: 
	XMERTL_ROOT=Your_EMERTL_ROOT_PATH
	such as:
	XMERTL_ROOT=/home/gits/xmertl-4.0-rc1	
start_test.sh
	XMERTL_ROOT=Your_EMERTL_ROOT_PATH
	such as:
	XMERTL_ROOT=/home/gits/xmertl-4.0-rc1	

When you finish the enviroment setting. You can do the test same bellow.


# make
# ./start_test.sh


